A backend REST API built using Django REST Framework that allows users to manage tasks securely using JWT authentication and PostgreSQL as the database.

This project focuses on backend best practices including authentication, authorization, database integration, and API testing.

ğŸš€ Features

JWT-based user authentication
Secure, user-specific task management
CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
PostgreSQL database integration
Environment variable-based configuration
API testing using Postman

